Installed Node.js version 20.16 using nvm:


curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash


Exited the terminal using the exit command, then reopened it. Activated nvm and installed Node.js:


nvm install 20.16
nvm use 20.16


Verified Node.js and npm installation:


node -v
npm -v


Installed SASS globally:


npm install -g sass


Verified SASS installation:


sass --version
